beer.beer_description:
The Riverland’s only craft brewery,
and only coffee roaster, team up
again to produce this second
edition of Firehouse Coffee Stout.
Arrosto coffee have been working
on a cold extract method to
produce a clean and fresh coffee
flavour, using their award winning
Engine 152 blend.
Brewed with seven malts of barley
and wheat, and hopped with
classic EK Goldings, we brew
